<p>Ledger is extending its wallet management app Ledger Live to also include a crypto exchange on board.</p>

<p>This is a standard feature of all the <a href="/altcoin-wallets/">user-friendly crypto wallets</a>, we already know it from Exodus &amp; co.</p>

<p>Ledger is now offering a 25 USD voucher for crypto purchase to every Ledger Nano X purchase.</p>

<p><strong>If you want to give crypto as a Christmas gift, this is a nice way to do it.</strong></p>

<p><a class="btn" href="https://bit.ly/2VCRTgb">Go to Ledger Christmas offer</a></p>

